result.title: **Award Winning** Sci-Fi Short  Film: "The Surface" - by Willem Kampenhout | TheCGBros
result.description:
In a grim apocalyptic future where mankind lives underground, a woman struggles to save her son from dying of mechanical lung failure. After all other options fail, her only hope is to venture to the desolate surface and face the ferocious monsters that drove mankind below! For more information, please see the details and links below:


More Info Available at: www.thesurfaceshort.com
IMDB: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt5287818/


Written and Directed by: Willem Kampenhout
Produced by: Kirsten Anderson
Edited by: Peter Walton
Cinematography by: Jarom Cowan
Production Designer: Ashley Cook
Music by: Danny Gray
Sound Design by: Adrian Maruri
Visual Effects Supervisor: Willem Kampenhout
See full credit list at the end of the film

This film was made as a capstone project at Brigham Young University.
